===================
Yum dependencies
===================

To check the dependencies of a specific installed package:
# rpm -qR <package_name>
To see the packages installed due to a specific package:
To find out which packages were installed as dependencies when installing a specific package, you can use the -qi option to display information about the package, including its installation history:

# rpm -qi <package_name>

# repoquery -q --installed --whatrequires freetype-2.9.1-
# repoquery -q --installed --whatrequires grub2-tools-

